                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#7C3AED" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2"/><rect x="9" y="3" width="6" height="4" rx="2"/><line x1="9" y1="12" x2="15" y2="12"/><line x1="9" y1="16" x2="13" y2="16"/></svg>
                Valid Dictionary Words Not in Today's Official Answers
