          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm mb-3">The maximum possible score for this puzzle is <strong>{totalPoints} points</strong>. Four-letter words earn 1 point each, while longer words earn points equal to their letter count. Pangrams receive a bonus 7 points on top of their letter-count score. To reach Genius level, you need <strong>{geniusThreshold} points</strong> (70% of the total).</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm mb-3">Word lengths in today's Bee range from 4 to {sortedLengths[0] || '?'} letters. {sortedLengths.length > 0 ? `The most common word length is ${sortedLengths.reduce((a, b) => wordsByLength[a].length >= wordsByLength[b].length ? a : b)}-letter words with ${wordsByLength[sortedLengths.reduce((a, b) => wordsByLength[a].length >= wordsByLength[b].length ? a : b)].length} entries.` : ''} The center letter {center} appears in every single word, while the outer letters each appear in a varying number of answers.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">SbSolver provides the complete word list, pangram details, and scoring breakdown for every daily Spelling Bee puzzle. Whether you're stuck on a few words or want to verify your progress, our tool gives you instant access to today's full solution set without any subscription or paywall.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Section -->
